<br>
Is this indeed the case?  If so, FIX IT! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uvariathemage.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Varia the mage</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#333333>(8/15/02 11:30:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=902.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: FLOWING THOUGHT</span><hr size=1> This might have been the case at one point, but isn't anymore.  There have been many tests to confirm it is working correctly, I believe by Graffie's (sp?).<br>
 <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=108671>Varia Darselai</a> Arch Mage
<br>
<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=110669>Milaril</a> 53rd monk</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/uadonhiram.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Adonhiram</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#333333>(8/16/02 6:55:47 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=902.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: FLOWING THOUGHT</span><hr size=1> Correct, and Verant confirmed it officially.<br>
<br>
(+) FT of same level NOW stack.<br>
<br>
(-) Any mana perma-regen from items COUNTS for the FT cap of 15. So if you have, let's say, the 8th shawl, effect &quot;Zephyr of Brell&quot; (combination of FT2 and extended enhancement III), thought it is not tagged FT, the 2mana/tick count for reaching the total of 15.<br>
<br>
But let's face it, to reach the 15 cap, you have to be in a pretty strong guild, as high FT items mainly are non-drop loot from Luclin boss or mini boss mobs which require a rather large and well equipped raid force. Not many 60 mages are coming close to the cap of 15.<br>
<br>
It is easy to find FT1, FT2, even FT3 (CT boots), but FT4+ is something which is pretty rare. And don't forget we also have to look for good items which have our summoned items effects (or other effects, like enshrouded veil for Summoning Efficiency), and you won't find items which have two effects.<br>
<br>
Basically it is either FT or a focus effect, except for some very high level drops (Luclin robes for some of them), or for 8th shwal whioch has a combo as I said.<br>
<br>
No worries ... <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showPrevMessage?topicID=902.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showNextMessage?topicID=902.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=902.topic&index=2><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.threadControl?topicID=902.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=902.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm28.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=902.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncements">Administration<option value="themagicianstowergeneral">General<option value="themagicianstowerfrm32">Class Balance<option value="themagicianstowerfrm45">User Interface<option value="themagicianstowerspells">Spells<option value="themagicianstowerequipmentandquests">Quests<option value="themagicianstowerfrm28">Equipment<option value="themagicianstowerfrm29">Magician Pets<option value="themagicianstowerfrm30">Magician 